data.description: Fantastic Upper-Level Unit in the Gated Ponderosa West Community! Living room w/ soaring vaulted ceilings & balcony w/ fantastic treetop views. Kitchen w/ hardwood cabinets. Dining area w/ pendant lamp. Spacious Bedroom w/ walk-in closet. Washer/dryer in unit. 1 assigned carport space w/ plenty of guest parking. Association amenities include swimming pools/spas, paid water/trash, & beautifully landscaped grounds w/ mature foliage & streams throughout. Centrally located - just minutes to the best shopping, dining, & entertainment the area has to offer.
